            <title><![CDATA[Dying Light: The Beast Gets Detailed PC Requirements; NVIDIA DLSS 4, AMD FSR 4, Intel XeSS 2 Confirmed]]></title>
            <link>https://wccftech.com/dying-light-the-beast-pc-requirements-nvidia-dlss-4-amd-fsr-4-intel-xess-2/</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/dying-light-the-beast-gets-detailed-pc-requirements-nvidia-dlss-4-amd-fsr-4-intel-xess-2-confirmed.1286574/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

			

			
			
			
			<p>Today, Techland has confirmed the final PC system requirements for Dying Light: The Beast. The new entry in the popular first-person open world action zombie game was originally scheduled to launch on August 22, but the Polish studio <a href="https://wccftech.com/dying-light-the-beast-receives-four-week-delay/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">announced</a> a slight delay to September 19 in order to apply more refinements and tweaks.</p>



<p>The requirements are quite a bit higher than those of Techland's previous game, 2022's Dying Light 2: Stay Human, indirectly confirming the upgrade of the underlying Chrome Engine that the developers have been touting.</p>



<figure><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td><strong>MINIMUM</strong></td><td><strong>RECOMMENDED</strong></td><td><strong>HIGH</strong></td><td><strong>ULTRA</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>PERFORMANCE</strong></td><td>1080p 30FPS</td><td>1440p 60FPS</td><td>4K 60FPS</td><td>4K 60FPS</td></tr><tr><td><strong>GRAPHIC SETTINGS</strong></td><td>LOW</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>HIGH</td><td>ULTRA (RT W/ FRAME GENERATION)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>GPU</strong></td><td>NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 - AMD Radeon RX 5500 XT - Intel Arc A750</td><td>NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3070 TI - AMD Radeon RX 6750 XT - Intel Arc B580</td><td>NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070 TI - AMD Radeon RX 7900 GRE</td><td>NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5070 AMD -  Radeon RX 9070 -  Intel Arc B580</td></tr><tr><td><strong>GPU MEMORY</strong></td><td>6GB</td><td>8GB</td><td>12GB</td><td>12GB</td></tr><tr><td><strong>CPU</strong></td><td>Intel i5-13400F -AMD Ryzen 7 5800F</td><td>Intel i5-13400F - AMD Ryzen 7 7700</td><td>Intel i7-13700K -AMD Ryzen 9 7800 X3D</td><td>Intel i9-14900K - AMD Ryzen 9 7950X3D</td></tr><tr><td><strong>RAM</strong></td><td>16GB</td><td>16GB</td><td>32GB</td><td>32GB</td></tr><tr><td><strong>OS</strong></td><td>Windows 10 or newer</td><td>Windows 10 or newer</td><td>Windows 10 or newer</td><td>Windows 10 or newer</td></tr><tr><td><strong>STORAGE</strong></td><td>70 GB SSD</td><td>70 GB SSD</td><td>70 GB SSD</td><td>70 GB SSD</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p>When it comes to features, the game will support all the latest upscalers from NVIDIA, AMD, and Intel, and other features, such as NVIDIA Reflex 2:</p>



<ul>
<li>Raytraced Global Illumination and Reflections</li>



<li>Ultra-wide resolution support</li>



<li>Upscaler and Frame Generation: Intel XeSS 2, NVIDIA DLSS 4, and AMD FSR 3.1 &amp; 4 (on select devices)</li>



<li>Latency Optimization: NVIDIA Reflex 2, AMD AntiLag 2, and Intel Xe Low Latency</li>



<li>In-depth customization options</li>
</ul>



<p>Interestingly, Techland has released separate Dying Light: The Beast specs for PC laptops.</p>



<figure><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td><strong>MINIMUM</strong></td><td><strong>RECOMMENDED</strong></td><td><strong>HIGH</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>PERFORMANCE</strong></td><td>1080p 30FPS</td><td>1080p 60FPS</td><td>1440p 60FPS</td></tr><tr><td><strong>GRAPHIC SETTINGS</strong></td><td>LOW</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>HIGH</td></tr><tr><td><strong>GPU</strong></td><td>NVIDIA GEFORCE RTX 3050 80W+ Laptop -AMD Ryzen AI 7 350 / 360 - INTEL CORE ULTRA 7 258V WITH ARC 140V</td><td>NVIDIA GEFORCE RTX 3080 Laptop - AMD RYZEN Al 9 370</td><td>NVIDIA GEFORCE RTX 4070 Laptop - AMD RYZEN Al MAX+ 395</td></tr><tr><td><strong>GPU MEMORY</strong></td><td>6GB</td><td>8GB</td><td>8GB</td></tr><tr><td><strong>CPU</strong></td><td>INTEL CORE i5-12450H - AMD RYZEN 5 6600H - INTEL CORE ULTRA 7 258V WITH ARC 140V</td><td>INTEL CORE i7-12700H - AMD RYZEN 7 6800H</td><td>INTEL CORE i7-14700HX - AMD RYZEN 9 8940HX</td></tr><tr><td><strong>RAM</strong></td><td>16GB</td><td>16GB</td><td>32GB</td></tr><tr><td><strong>OS</strong></td><td>WINDOWS 10 OR NEWER</td><td>WINDOWS 10 OR NEWER</td><td>WINDOWS 10 OR NEWER</td></tr><tr><td><strong>STORAGE</strong></td><td>70 GB SSD</td><td>70 GB SSD</td><td>70 GB SSD</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



